Description:  Provides a modular, extensible framework to simulate and play Blackjack in R. 
    Supports multiple players, interactive and programmatic play, standard and custom rules, 
    and full set of player actions (hit, stand, split, double down, surrender, insurance). 
    Includes S3 and vctrs support for custom card vectors, well-documented workflows, 
    and robust result objects for analysis or teaching.
